Day 1 Solution Steps:
Install browser extensions like ‘edit this cookie’ or any other cookie manager browser add
After login to the site - click on the add to view the cookie name (key) with just a one click - rather that going into the dev tools
Copy the auth cookie value and navigate to the cyberchef site https://gchq.github.io/CyberChef/ paste the same - a magic stick will appear click on it - it will show the encoded format and the decoded value below
The decoded value is in key:value pair in ‘JSON’ format
Replace your username in the decoded value with ‘santa’ value and encode the same with ‘Hex’
Copy paste the resulted value into your auth cookie and refresh the site - boom! You will logged in as santa user - activate all the button to get the flags 

